I wanted to bring up the torment line of spells.<br>
Last night I turned in my spectral, hoping for a &quot;Night Terror&quot; scarecrow special instead I got a <!--EZCODE UNDERLINE START--><span style="text-decoration:underline">Torment of Scio</span><!--EZCODE UNDERLINE END-->.<br>
<br>
What good is this line of spells?  It's suppose to reduce the mob's wis and int while depleading the mob's mana pool and hp by 40 pts per tick.<br>
<br>
Uhhhh, this doesn't seem all that useful when you're putting a dot on mobs that are packing thousands of hps and thousands of mana.<br>
<br>
Hoping for some enlightment. Thxs!<br>
<br>
