 <br>
It is a nice suppliment to the mana sieve which has I believe about a 10 second recast time.<br>
<br>
If you stack scryer's trespass and Scio you get a mana drain of 95 a tick then add mana sieve and a ToT depending on the lenght of the battle-you can render a gating mob useless usually within the course of the encounter again depending on the dps of the raid/group you are in.<br>
<br>
Found this most handy in HoT when fighting gating/cheal mobs as we are fairly small guild that does this area with 7 to 9 people it is imperative that I get this mobs OOM which I can quite handly before the mob even reaches 50% health.<br>
<br>
Just my view the spell and  how I use it. <br>
If you have a raid that does huge dps then there really is no point to even mana draining a mob as you will not have time to drain it  unless you have same for example 5 chanters all mana sieving it.<br>
